---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About | NaughtyCamSpot"
  description="Learn how NaughtyCamSpot empowers models with technology, concierge strategy, and premium affiliate partnerships."
>
  <section class="hero-shell parallax-veil">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-black/60 via-transparent to-black/70"></div>
    <div class="relative space-y-6">
      <span class="hero-tagline">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl leading-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">Empowering Models Through Technology.</h1>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-base text-white/70">
        NaughtyCamSpot is a concierge growth collective for models who crave polish, strategy, and sustainable income. We blend
        human-led mentorship with AI-driven insights so you can perform with confidence and scale with intention.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="content-card space-y-4">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Mission Statement</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        We exist to elevate cam performers into luxury creators--artists with the business infrastructure, coaching, and production
        support they deserve. Our team obsesses over every layer of the viewer journey, translating psychology and hospitality into
        simple, repeatable systems.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="content-card space-y-4">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Our Technology</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        From AI-assisted scripting to automated recap dashboards, our stack keeps you in the loop without overwhelm. You will know
        when to trigger tip trains, which segments crave exclusives, and which storytelling beats resonate most.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card space-y-6">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Affiliate Partners</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
      We amplify your reach through curated alliances. Expect best-in-class support from platforms that respect your craft and
      reward your hustle.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">
      <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">CamSoda</span>
      <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">Chaturbate</span>
      <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">CrakRevenue</span>
      <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">ExoClick</span>
      <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">Streamate</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card space-y-4">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Founder Note</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
      "We built NaughtyCamSpot to be the agency we wished existed when we started. Our models aren't just performers; they're
      entrepreneurs with signature brands. We simply provide the infrastructure, the storytelling, and the protection to help them
      grow without burning out." -- Lola Cuevas, Founder
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
